text: Na Svatém Kopečku is a 1934 Czechoslovak musical comedy film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Jaroslav Vojta, Marie Grossová, and Jiřina Steimarová. ==Cast== *Jaroslav Vojta as Holeček, farmer *Marie Grossová as Mája Malínská *Jiřina Steimarová as Heda *Valentin Šindler as Matej Krópal from Brochovany *Rudolf Lampa *Světla Svozilová as Běta *Ladislav Pešek *Jindřich Plachta as Jakub *Zdeňka Baldová as Králová *Václav Trégl as Portýr *Jaroslav Bráška *Josef Kotalík *Bohumil Mottl ==References== ==External links== *Na Svatém Kopečku at the Internet Movie Database Category:1934 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak musical comedy films Category:1934 musical comedy films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black-and-white films Category:1934 comedy films
